					About TriMas				








				About TriMas			


We are a diversified manufacturer of engineered products that serve a variety of industrial, commercial and consumer end markets worldwide. Our family of businesses provide customers with innovative product solutions under well-recognized brands and have leadership positions in the niche markets they serve. TriMas has approximately 4,000 employees in 12 countries and is headquartered in Bloomfield Hills, Michigan. TriMas shares are listed on NASDAQ under the ticker symbol TRS. 







